---
title: Heirloom Tomato Flatbread with Fresh Mozzarella & Pesto
description: It’s hard to go wrong with fresh mozzarella, vibrant heirloom tomatoes, and herby pesto. We’re letting these ingredients shine in a simple flatbread recipe that couldn’t be easier to prepare. If you know you’ll be making this recipe in advance, let your dough come to room temperature for a few hours—it’ll be easier to roll out!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/556f5ab5fd2cb9bf198b4567.jpg
